<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Verification Approved</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      min-width: 100%;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      background-color: #f4f7f6;
      color: #333333;
    }

    a {
      color: #0070f3;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #fff;
    }

    p {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #555555;
    }

    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    .email-header {
      background-color: #0070f3;
      padding: 24px;
      color: #ffffff;
      border-top-left-radius: 8px;
      border-top-right-radius: 8px;
    }

    .email-body {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .email-footer {
      background-color: #f6f6f6;
      padding: 24px;
      border-bottom-left-radius: 8px;
      border-bottom-right-radius: 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Verification Approved</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Hello <%= user.username %>,</p>
      <p>Your verification request has been approved.</p>
      <p>You are now verified as both a Freelancer and a Client.</p>
      <p>Thank you for joining us!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a
          href="mailto:musamuhammedolayinka@gmail.com">Support</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>